extends layout

block content
  section.page-header
    .container
      h1.page-title About Alex Thompson
      p.page-subtitle Passionate photographer dedicated to capturing life's most precious moments

  section.about-story
    .container
      .about-content
        .about-text
          h2 My Journey
          p Photography has been my passion for over eight years. What started as a hobby during college has evolved into a full-time career that brings me immense joy and fulfillment. I believe that every moment has a story to tell, and my mission is to capture those stories in their most authentic form.
          
          p My approach to photography is rooted in building genuine connections with my clients. I take the time to understand your vision, your story, and what makes each moment special to you. Whether it's the nervous excitement before a wedding ceremony, the quiet intimacy of a family gathering, or the professional confidence needed for corporate headshots, I'm there to capture it all.
          
          blockquote
            p "Photography is not just about taking pictures; it's about preserving emotions, memories, and the essence of who we are in that particular moment in time."
            cite - Alex Thompson
          
          p When I'm not behind the camera, you can find me exploring new locations for shoots, experimenting with new techniques, or spending time with my own family. I understand the importance of the moments I'm entrusted to capture because I cherish those same moments in my own life.

        .about-image
          img(src="/images/about-photographer.jpg", alt="Alex Thompson at work")

  section.experience
    .container
      h2.section-title Experience & Expertise
      .experience-grid
        .experience-item
          .experience-icon
            i.fas.fa-camera
          h3 Professional Equipment
          p State-of-the-art cameras and lighting equipment to ensure the highest quality results in any setting.
        
        .experience-item
          .experience-icon
            i.fas.fa-award
          h3 Award-Winning Work
          p Recognized by industry peers and featured in photography publications for creative excellence.
        
        .experience-item
          .experience-icon
            i.fas.fa-heart
          h3 Personal Approach
          p Every client receives personalized attention and a customized photography experience.
        
        .experience-item
          .experience-icon
            i.fas.fa-clock
          h3 Timely Delivery
          p Quick turnaround times without compromising on quality or attention to detail.

  section.skills
    .container
      .skills-content
        .skills-text
          h2 Photography Specializations
          p Over the years, I've developed expertise in various photography styles, each requiring unique skills and approaches:
          
          .skill-list
            .skill-item
              h4 Portrait Photography
              p Capturing personality and emotion in individual and group portraits
            
            .skill-item
              h4 Wedding Photography
              p Documenting love stories from engagement to the big day
            
            .skill-item
              h4 Event Photography
              p Professional coverage of corporate events, parties, and celebrations
            
            .skill-item
              h4 Landscape Photography
              p Showcasing the beauty of natural environments and cityscapes

        .skills-stats
          .stat-circle
            .stat-number 98%
            .stat-label Client Satisfaction
          .stat-circle
            .stat-number 500+
            .stat-label Projects Completed
          .stat-circle
            .stat-number 50+
            .stat-label Weddings Captured

  section.philosophy
    .container
      .philosophy-content
        h2 Photography Philosophy
        .philosophy-grid
          .philosophy-item
            h3 Authenticity First
            p I believe the best photographs come from genuine moments. I focus on capturing real emotions and natural interactions rather than forced poses.
          
          .philosophy-item
            h3 Storytelling Through Images
            p Every photo should tell a story. I work to understand the narrative of each event or session to create images that truly represent the moment.
          
          .philosophy-item
            h3 Collaborative Process
            p Photography is a collaborative art. I work closely with my clients to understand their vision and bring it to life through my lens.

  section.education
    .container
      h2.section-title Education & Training
      .timeline
        .timeline-item
          .timeline-date 2020
          .timeline-content
            h3 Advanced Wedding Photography Certification
            p Completed intensive training in wedding photography techniques and client management
        
        .timeline-item
          .timeline-date 2018
          .timeline-content
            h3 Studio Lighting Workshop
            p Mastered professional studio lighting techniques and portrait photography
        
        .timeline-item
          .timeline-date 2016
          .timeline-content
            h3 Bachelor of Fine Arts in Photography
            p Graduated with honors from the School of Visual Arts
        
        .timeline-item
          .timeline-date 2015
          .timeline-content
            h3 Started Professional Photography
            p Launched Alex Thompson Photography and began serving clients

  section.about-cta
    .container
      .cta-content
        h2 Let's Create Something Beautiful Together
        p Ready to capture your special moments? I'd love to hear about your photography needs and discuss how we can bring your vision to life.
        a.btn.btn-primary(href="/contact") Get In Touch